+	depends on DRM_DW_HDMI
 	depends on DRM_RCAR_DU || COMPILE_TEST
-	select DRM_DW_HDMI
 	help
 	  Enable support for R-Car Gen3 or RZ/G2 internal HDMI encoder.
 
